<b>Białas</b> (see   Bialas  ), Slovenian   Belec  , or any other synonymous Slavic surname beginning with <i>Bel-</i>, <i>Bev-</i>, <i>Biel-</i> or <i>Bil-</i>."]}]},{"name":"Mrs","type":"FIRST","attribution":"Dictionary of First Names © Patrick Hanks and Flavia Hodges 1990, 2003, 2006.","meanings":["from Latin <i>Ursus</i> ‘bear’."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Mrs Whyte had at least 1 son and 1 daughter with Mr Whyte."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","1480–Male":"1480–Surnud","1500–Female":"1500–Surnud","1516–1564":"1516–1564","–Female":"Surnud","1500":"1500","1564":"1564","about 1500":"umbes 1500","1480":"1480","ABT 1516":"umbes 1516","1516":"1516","Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland","Of, Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Šotimaa, United Kingdom"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","1480–Male":"1480–Kuollut","1500–Female":"1500–Kuollut","1516–1564":"1516–1564","–Female":"Kuollut","1500":"1500","1564":"1564","about 1500":"noin 1500","1480":"1480","ABT 1516":"noin 1516","1516":"1516","Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland","Of, Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Skotlanti, Yhdistynyt kuningaskunta"},"fr":{"–":"Décédée","1480–Male":"1480–Décédé","1500–Female":"1500–Décédée","1516–1564":"1516–1564","–Female":"Décédée","1500":"1500","1564":"1564","about 1500":"environ 1500","1480":"1480","ABT 1516":"environ 1516","1516":"1516","Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Écosse","Of, Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Écosse, Royaume-Uni","lifeSummary":"Mrs Whyte a eu au moins 1 fils et 1 fille avec Mr Whyte."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","1480–Male":"1480–Verstorben","1500–Female":"1500–Verstorben","1516–1564":"1516–1564","–Female":"Verstorben","1500":"1500","1564":"1564","about 1500":"um 1500","1480":"1480","ABT 1516":"um 1516","1516":"1516","Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland","Of, Dunfermline, Fife, Scotland":"Dunfermline, Fife, Schottland, United Kingdom","lifeSummary":"Mrs Whyt